<p class="">Who is he?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a789cd41-0afe-463c-9b93-ba4442c63b71" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-a789cd41-0afe-463c-9b93-ba4442c63b71">
