            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4947269f-4f89-469b-8856-97932189712d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
