<p class="">He was doing the programme for Horlick's, which is not a laxative.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7ec7323b-31ba-4c94-8845-2d58242ebac8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
