        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ffa64899-0cd1-4304-a4cf-917f4eb1c802">
                The Assistant Postmaster-General (Mr. David Gammans)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
