               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-8960da20-9256-42b0-ab0e-378e5298b4b2">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I do not see how, in Canada, they can have taken a Gallup <span id="398" class="column-number" data-column-number="398"></span> poll comparing commercial television with the sort of television programme that the B.B.C. gives us. We have another hon. Gentleman from the same country with us, the hon. Member for Southgate (Mr. Baxter). If he would, for a minute or two, give us his opinions on the matter, and say whether he thinks that 90 per cent. of the Canadians take such a view, it would be of great benefit to the Committee.<p></p> The hon. Member for Bolton, East (Mr. Philip Bell) laughed at the suggestion in the letter which my hon. and learned Friend the Member for Gloucester (Mr. Turner-Samuels) read out that there would be "commercials" every few minutes. But I listened to the hon. and learned Member's own account, and apparently in a 30-minute programme there are to be six minutes of advertisingâ€”one minute to five minutes of programme time. It seems to me to be the same thing as saying "every few minutes" if for every five minutes one listens to a programme one has to have one minute of advertising, according to the hon. and learned Member's own figures which he had not written down before him but which, nevertheless, we can take on trust.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8960da20-9256-42b0-ab0e-378e5298b4b2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-8960da20-9256-42b0-ab0e-378e5298b4b2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





