        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">If the hon. Gentleman had been present yesterday, he would realise that it is already in HANSARD.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-cbf6b569-88c5-40c0-858a-25a9f495d871" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-cbf6b569-88c5-40c0-858a-25a9f495d871">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
