        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I did not say that. Someone said that I had done something, and I said that I had not.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1e25d3a8-e621-489b-b7d5-eca22e7dd9e6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-1e25d3a8-e621-489b-b7d5-eca22e7dd9e6">
