    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-ba3c3e6b-c700-4e09-9948-c3a6c36420f8">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ba3c3e6b-c700-4e09-9948-c3a6c36420f8">
                Mr. A. Woodburn  (Clackmannan and East Stirlingshire)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ba3c3e6b-c700-4e09-9948-c3a6c36420f8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-ba3c3e6b-c700-4e09-9948-c3a6c36420f8">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The right hon. and learned Gentleman has tried to lubricate the passage of his Bill with his usual good humour and courtesy, but it is quite obvious from his failure to answer the hon. Member for Brighton that in defending the Bill he is up against great difficulties. It is a purely selfish Bill designed to bring profit to the highly populated City of London while the rest of the country can go "phut." There is not the slightest doubt about that. The right hon. and learned Gentleman has done his best to get round the point, but he has failed to answer the hon. Member for Brighton. Indeed, the hon. Member for Brighton in his earlier speechâ€”</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ba3c3e6b-c700-4e09-9948-c3a6c36420f8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
