    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I suggest that with this Amendment could be taken the-Amendments in line 8, leave out "industry, trade, finance," and insert "public service."<p></p> In line 8, after "administration," insert "the organisation of workers."<p></p> In line 8, at the end, insert, "television."<p></p> In line 8, at the end, insert "broadcasting."</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3ccd0f46-d4d4-4f6d-bd40-270fc48eb75f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-05-05/debates/d852ccb9-f914-450a-a605-c21e005963d4/Clause1%E2%80%94(TheIndependentTelevisionAuthority)#contribution-3ccd0f46-d4d4-4f6d-bd40-270fc48eb75f">
