<p class="">Could the hon. and learned Member give us his authority for that statement?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d9881ea0-0d6d-41a1-a8f9-37e21badad3a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
